OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 02 APR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2020FJust before 6am, UTV announcer
OL,7,FGillian Porter informs viewers in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland that dedicated UTV
OL,9,Fcontinuity is being suspended, due to
OL,10,Foperational changes resulting from the
OL,11,Fongoing coronavirus crisis.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe change was said to be temporary.
OL,14,
OL,15,FBut on 26th November 2020, ITV
OL,16,Fannounced that UTV continuity and 2016
OL,17,F- 2020 levels of associated UTV
OL,18,Fbranding would not return.
OL,19,
OL,20,FITV continuity/branding would become
OL,21,Fpermanent in Northern Ireland, with the
OL,22,Fexception of UTV branding for local
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
